<template>
  <form>
    <label for="new-todo-input"> What needs to be done? </label>
    <input
  type="text"
  id="new-todo-input"
  name="new-todo"
  autocomplete="off"
  v-model="label"
/>

    <button type="submit">Add</button>
  </form>
</template>


<script>
export default {
  methods: {
    onSubmit() {
      console.log("form submitted");
    },
  },
  data() {
    return {
      label: "",
    };
  },
};

</script>
